{"tid":1551371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太子比人清哂d花，DLLM","createTime":"2019-09-08T03:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:46:45.000Z","uid":197985,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9eac8b351d119a7bfc13e2e089189965a501cbd5","tid":1551371,"uid":197985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaZmu9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaZmu9m.jpg&h=c88268b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95bee179ddd83032efa7786591905e96f41d9185","tid":1551371,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a6db13499f59064d55bf94bfbcfcc4e3fa6297","tid":1551371,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識唱嘅大家一齊唱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《願榮光歸香港》  </strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">As we yearn, our freedom nighs</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With eyes blinded, long it comes the night</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight</span><br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!</span><br />\n捍自由   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We shall strike</span><br />\n來齊集這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">This perilous night</span><br />\n來全力抗對  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With hope, with song, with dignity!</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4kAzyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4kAzyW.jpg&h=84f48da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英文譯版原post<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》英文歌詞 &quot;Glory be to Thee, Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547782\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547782</a></span>"},{"pid":"5129987418503950ff9ff46f967a74a1931b2787","tid":1551371,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eac8b351d119a7bfc13e2e089189965a501cbd5","tid":1551371,"uid":197985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaZmu9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaZmu9m.jpg&h=c88268b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"過左頭7就清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a0450fa657ccdfa94e40ed5b6dc8210a9dc112","tid":1551371,"uid":304435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"佢唔清 我地又點再去擺呢？"},{"pid":"4d6d0d941cf5081e32c4910bb29f258152fb33be","tid":1551371,"uid":191776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"我知你嬲呀，但花死花還在呀，<br />\n<br />\n一陣中環見<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油"},{"pid":"a90adb94e546dcc416b1945c6f148d5d53be7e8c","tid":1551371,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"行過要播地藏菩薩超度心咒喔"},{"pid":"dd8c9a61527d75548597b85a71ba555966790cf9","tid":1551371,"uid":262597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"再獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9806d6f698e196d9783e95a1fa7ee031e8d75a","tid":1551371,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"應承我呢世都唔會原諒香港警察"},{"pid":"045f98c302609220f15aa1768c9f3e2c358d9640","tid":1551371,"uid":109581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"原post:<br />\n（請廣傳）  [可靠通靈訊息-831太子站]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549801</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明⋯ 亦了解你地會覺得好荒謬⋯⋯<br />\n咩料丫⋯⋯通靈⋯⋯？！<br />\n鏗鏘集都講左喇⋯⋯⋯<br />\n但老老實實⋯TVB嘅野信得過嗎？？<br />\n<br />\n短短幾日點解咁多人自殺？咁多屍體發現？<br />\n大家唔覺得奇怪？<br />\n<br />\n[大整合] 831事件未必得2個死(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544700</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力⋯<br />\n我唔係要求你信⋯ <br />\n但希望大家一齊用不同方法去求證⋯<br />\n<br />\n太子站成日封站⋯ 就算CCTV公開⋯<br />\n會唔會巳被人做左手腳重拍⋯ 邊個知？<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足繼續秉承不篤灰、不割席、不分化、不指摘，<br />\n去到地鐵站自己fact check 感覺下⋯⋯<br />\n住西環嘅留意下域多利亞公眾殮房⋯<br />\n如果你有朋友有陰陽眼⋯ 請佢睇睇⋯<br />\n如果你識能人異士，請佢發表下⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n務求能讓事件真相大白，義士能尋冤得雪⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（請廣傳）<br />\n<br />\n[可靠通靈訊息-831太子站]<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n正當香港政府嚴正聲明831太子站清場期間没有被捕者傷亡。有資深通靈人士表示，單單831，<br />\n已<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有11名死者</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屍體並已被不同方法處理。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其中9名死者:<br />\n<br />\n1. 男士，15-16歳，死後被列作跳樓個案<br />\n<br />\n2. 女士，17-18歳，tomboy<br />\n<br />\n3. 細路仔，在列車車頭位置被打死<br />\n<br />\n4.男士，2x歳，其女朋友在彌留狀態<br />\n<br />\n5. 男士，4x歳，放工路過，為保護其他傷者而被打死<br />\n<br />\n6. 男士，4x歳，死後被列作浮屍發現案處理<br />\n<br />\n7. 男士，21歳，跳閘時走不及被扑死，屍體被埋<br />\n<br />\n8. 男士，屍體被冷藏，在域多利亞公眾殮房<br />\n<br />\n9. 男士，3x歳，帶眼鏡<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">或者你會問⋯⋯⋯<br />\n點解屋企人/ 朋友/ 同事唔去搵佢地～<br />\n</span></span><br />\n我自己都分析過，有唔同既可能性，純屬推測:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 家人被滅聲<br />\n2. 家人被綑綁囚禁<br />\n3. 送了上大陸<br />\n4. 被殺後成為其他死亡個案<br />\n5. 政府介入，例如指使學校岀信，扮成自殺個案<br />\n6. 如果家人報警，警察問失蹤者是否當日有示威？<br />\n    再搵返時都會被控暴動罪。家人會唔會唔敢出聲？</span><br />\n<br />\n加上昨日新聞⋯⋯<br />\n有朋友失蹤，佢想搵朋友，但連佢父母都⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n【突發】 HKFP意外拍攝到太子站女死者朋友：死者父母要求取回屍體被軟禁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548108</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2413012775647133&amp;id=1648246202123798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2413012775647133%26id%3D1648246202123798&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=f60916a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2413012775647133&amp;id=1648246202123798</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfp/videos/513572885882550?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongfp%2Fvideos%2F513572885882550%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=d5e2ab61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfp/videos/513572885882550?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係好令人懷疑⋯⋯⋯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係得一個人話見到太子站有野⋯⋯<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1546911/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1546911/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDzBiXe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDzBiXe.png&h=e69ff5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/757857310941980/posts/2556568487737511?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F757857310941980%2Fposts%2F2556568487737511%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=dcdc0e38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/757857310941980/posts/2556568487737511?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2yuDXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2yuDXJ.png&h=455f0038&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0USGu4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0USGu4o.png&h=49b09595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">短短幾日內點解咁多自殺？<br />\n大家有冇諗過？ <br />\n係被自殺？？而且數字不斷增加⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【細思極恐】北角浮屍案位死者到底係點死？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549796</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkWzP4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkWzP4z.jpg&h=96eec6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我搵過多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">域多利亞公眾殮房</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9F%9F%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%AE%AE%E6%88%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259F%259F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%25AE%25AE%25E6%2588%25BF&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=fa3270f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9F%9F%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%AE%AE%E6%88%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n有個咁的新聞丫⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n主管五度犯錯 未等家屬認屍<br />\n域多利亞殮房擅葬遺體<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20070927/20070927024639_0000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fnews%2F20070927%2F20070927024639_0000.html&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7ad85eea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20070927/20070927024639_0000.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以⋯⋯⋯<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家請幫幫手⋯<br />\n唔理你係咩宗教信仰⋯⋯<br />\n大家只求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真相</span>～！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，<br />\n秉承不篤灰、不割席、<br />\n不分化、不指摘，<br />\n「五大訴求，決一不可」<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n「香港人 加油」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">P牌仔推唔郁⋯⋯<br />\n請廣傳～～</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993c7ecaec61418c1c7a15fa657c7f384391a4ac","tid":1551371,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"【致所有政客們】香港人給你的忠告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母忘死去的烈士<br />\n母忘服役的義士<br />\n母忘失蹤的手足<br />\n母忘受傷的手足<br />\n母忘待判的手足<br />\n母忘流亡的手足"}]}